1
00:00:47,480 --> 00:00:48,513
[ PANTING ]

2
00:00:48,547 --> 00:00:50,282
[ PANTING ]

3
00:00:52,785 --> 00:00:54,254
[ GRUNTS ]

4
00:00:58,691 --> 00:01:00,260
[ GRUNTS ]

5
00:01:05,564 --> 00:01:06,398
SHIT!

6
00:01:20,846 --> 00:01:22,715
AAH!

7
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:43,603
TELL THE SKINHEAD THANKS
FOR A JOB WELL DONE.

8
00:01:43,636 --> 00:01:45,405
MY PLEASURE.

9
00:01:49,441 --> 00:01:52,479
THERE'S A LITTLE BONUS
FOR YOU.

10
00:02:04,190 --> 00:02:07,360
IF YOU'RE GONNA PLAY WITH GUNS,
SOMEBODY'S GONNA GET HURT.

11
00:02:07,393 --> 00:02:09,428
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

12
00:02:09,461 --> 00:02:10,796
<i> HERE YOU GO, DUQUESNE --</i>

13
00:02:10,829 --> 00:02:13,599
<i> YOUR HALF
 OF THE SKINHEAD'S MONEY.</i>

14
00:02:13,632 --> 00:02:15,535
OKAY,
LET'S GET OUT OF HERE.

15
00:02:16,669 --> 00:02:18,872
[ HORNS HONKING ]

16
00:02:43,395 --> 00:02:45,398
BLADE AND DUQUESNE.

17
00:02:45,431 --> 00:02:47,934
<i> Garr: Okay.
 Send them in.</i>

18
00:03:39,418 --> 00:03:40,519
REPORT.

19
00:03:40,552 --> 00:03:42,555
UH, MISSION ACCOMPLISHED,
SIR.

20
00:03:42,588 --> 00:03:44,489
THE COP'S HISTORY.

21
00:03:45,958 --> 00:03:47,393
THANK YOU.

22
00:03:47,426 --> 00:03:48,628
GOODBYE.

23
00:04:11,917 --> 00:04:14,553
HERE! MOVE! COME ON!
COME HERE! MOVE IT!

24
00:04:14,586 --> 00:04:16,656
[ SIREN BLARING,
WOMAN SCREAMING ]

25
00:04:14,586 --> 00:04:16,656
<i> Man: DROP YOUR WEAPONS!</i>

26
00:04:16,689 --> 00:04:19,792
<i> I REPEAT --
 PUT DOWN YOUR WEAPONS!</i>

27
00:04:19,825 --> 00:04:22,428
<i> WE'VE GOT
 THE PLACE SURROUNDED!</i>

28
00:04:22,461 --> 00:04:24,030
YOU STAY BACK!
I'LL KILL HIM!

29
00:04:24,063 --> 00:04:25,798
I SWEAR,
I'LL KILL HIM!

30
00:04:25,831 --> 00:04:27,900
[ SCREAMS ]

31
00:04:25,831 --> 00:04:27,900
COME HERE!

32
00:04:27,933 --> 00:04:30,469
<i> DO NOT HARM THE HOSTAGES!</i>

33
00:04:27,933 --> 00:04:30,469
HEY!

34
00:04:30,502 --> 00:04:31,771
YOU STAY AWAY FROM ME!

35
00:04:31,804 --> 00:04:33,873
GET BACK
OR I'LL KILL HIM!

36
00:04:33,906 --> 00:04:35,474
QUIT SQUIRMING!

37
00:04:35,507 --> 00:04:37,343
GET DOWN!

38
00:04:37,376 --> 00:04:39,512
<i> DO NOT DO ANYTHING RASH!</i>

39
00:04:39,545 --> 00:04:41,480
<i> YOU MUST SURRENDER AT ONCE!</i>

40
00:04:39,545 --> 00:04:41,480
<i> WATCH THE WINDOWS!
 WATCH THE WINDOWS!</i>

41
00:04:41,513 --> 00:04:43,082
<i> THERE ARE NO ALTERNATIVES!</i>

42
00:04:43,115 --> 00:04:44,917
YOU WILL NEVER
GET AWAY WITH THIS!

43
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:47,053
<i> STUPID POLITICIAN,
 ALL YOU DO IS TAL!</i>

44
00:04:47,086 --> 00:04:48,888
LET'S SEE HOW WELL
YOU TALK WITHOUT A TONGUE!

45
00:04:48,921 --> 00:04:50,022
[ GUNSHOT ]

46
00:04:50,856 --> 00:04:52,558
[ SCREAMS ]

47
00:04:58,464 --> 00:04:59,432
COME ON!

48
00:04:59,465 --> 00:05:01,566
<i> WATCH YOUR BACK!</i>

49
00:04:59,465 --> 00:05:01,566
<i> COME ON!</i>

50
00:05:03,001 --> 00:05:05,371
<i> [ SCREAMS ]</i>

51
00:05:05,404 --> 00:05:07,540
<i> SHE'S HIT!</i>

52
00:05:15,514 --> 00:05:17,483
<i> COME ON!</i>

53
00:05:21,019 --> 00:05:23,856
[ LAUGHING ]

54
00:05:23,889 --> 00:05:25,491
SHE'S SUCH A HAM.

55
00:05:25,524 --> 00:05:26,826
[ BUZZER ]

56
00:05:26,859 --> 00:05:28,561
I HATE TO TELL YOU,
BUT THEY DON'T GIVE OSCARS

57
00:05:28,594 --> 00:05:30,963
FOR TRAINING FILMS.

58
00:05:28,594 --> 00:05:30,963
OH, THANK YOU. OOH!

59
00:05:30,996 --> 00:05:33,933
OKAY, BOYS,
LISTEN UP.

60
00:05:33,966 --> 00:05:36,001
THE MISTAKE
THAT WAS MADE HERE

61
00:05:36,034 --> 00:05:38,837
WAS THAT WHEN OUR MAN REED
DISARMED TANGO ONE,

62
00:05:38,871 --> 00:05:41,474
BUT HE TURNED HIS BACK
ON THE SITUATION,

63
00:05:41,507 --> 00:05:43,743
ALLOWING HIMSELF
TO BE BLINDSIDED.

64
00:05:43,776 --> 00:05:45,778
THIS IS PRETTY MUCH
HOW IT SHOULD HAVE GONE DOWN.

65
00:05:45,811 --> 00:05:48,381
UH, SERGEANT GILL, PLEASE?

66
00:05:48,414 --> 00:05:50,116
IF I MAY.

67
00:05:50,149 --> 00:05:53,119
OKAY,
AFTER REED DISARMED TANGO,

68
00:05:53,152 --> 00:05:54,486
HE SHOULD'VE PRESSED
THE ADVANTAGE,

69
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:56,455
KEEPING HIM OFF-BALANCE,

70
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:56,455
[ GRUNTING ]

71
00:05:56,488 --> 00:05:59,892
PUTTING HIM IN A SITUATION
WHERE HE COULD EITHER KILL HIM,

72
00:05:59,925 --> 00:06:01,394
USE HIM AS A SHIELD,

73
00:06:01,427 --> 00:06:04,163
AND TO VIEW THE SITUATION
AROUND HIM.

74
00:06:04,196 --> 00:06:06,165
ECONOMY OF MOVEMENT
IS THE KEY

75
00:06:06,198 --> 00:06:09,501
TO THESE CLOSE-QUARTERS
SITUATIONS.

76
00:06:09,535 --> 00:06:10,703
<i> Director: CUT!</i>

77
00:06:09,535 --> 00:06:10,703
[ EXHALES SLOWLY ]

78
00:06:10,736 --> 00:06:12,570
<i> THAT'S A PRINT.</i>

79
00:06:10,736 --> 00:06:12,570
GOOD JOB.

80
00:06:12,604 --> 00:06:13,739
THANKS.

81
00:06:13,772 --> 00:06:15,908
ALL RIGHT, GOOD JOB, GUYS.
CHEERS.

82
00:06:15,941 --> 00:06:17,743
THANKS, BUDDY.
YOU WORK FAST.

83
00:06:15,941 --> 00:06:17,743
[ LAUGHS ]

84
00:06:17,776 --> 00:06:19,078
<i> YOU LIKE THAT?</i>

85
00:06:19,111 --> 00:06:21,981
<i> OKAY, 7:00 AT THE DOG & HOUN.
 I'LL BE THERE.</i>

86
00:06:22,014 --> 00:06:24,150
ALL RIGHT.

87
00:06:24,183 --> 00:06:25,685
SQUAD!

88
00:06:26,952 --> 00:06:28,954
AT EASE, GENTLEMEN.

89
00:06:28,987 --> 00:06:30,523
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

90
00:06:30,556 --> 00:06:32,425
CAPTAIN MACKENZIE.

91
00:06:32,458 --> 00:06:34,660
CAPTAIN KELLY...

92
00:06:36,495 --> 00:06:38,531
WHAT'S WRONG?

93
00:06:36,495 --> 00:06:38,531
IT'S, UH...

94
00:06:38,564 --> 00:06:40,833
IT'S ABOUT
YOUR STEPBROTHER.

95
00:07:55,007 --> 00:07:56,976
YOU'RE ERIC?

96
00:07:58,243 --> 00:08:00,279
I'M VERONIQUE.

97
00:08:00,312 --> 00:08:03,082
I WAS SEEING
YOUR BROTHER.

98
00:08:03,115 --> 00:08:04,884
[ SIGHS SOFTLY ]

99
00:08:04,917 --> 00:08:07,119
I'M VERY SORRY.

100
00:08:14,860 --> 00:08:16,695
EXCUSE ME.

101
00:08:16,728 --> 00:08:19,165
DID SHE SAY SHE WAS
SEEING YOUR BROTHER?

102
00:08:20,265 --> 00:08:21,667
UH, YEAH, SHE DID.

103
00:08:27,706 --> 00:08:29,108
EXCUSE ME.

104
00:08:27,706 --> 00:08:29,108
WHAT?

105
00:08:29,141 --> 00:08:30,743
I'VE NEVER SEEN YOU BEFORE
IN MY LIFE.

106
00:08:32,144 --> 00:08:33,245
ERIC?

107
00:08:33,278 --> 00:08:34,712
<i> I'M MICHAEL DURKE.</i>

108
00:08:34,746 --> 00:08:36,582
SOLDIER'S LIEUTENANT.

109
00:08:36,615 --> 00:08:38,049
NICE TO MEET YOU.

110
00:08:38,082 --> 00:08:39,617
I WISH WE WOULD HAVE
MET UNDER...

111
00:08:39,650 --> 00:08:42,253
UNDER PLEASANT CIRCUMSTANCES.

112
00:08:42,287 --> 00:08:45,024
YEAH, I KNOW.
WELL, THANK YOU FOR COMING.

113
00:08:45,057 --> 00:08:47,693
THIS IS
DETECTIVE ELIZABETH HAMPTON.

114
00:08:47,726 --> 00:08:49,728
SHE WAS
SOLDIER'S PARTNER.

115
00:08:49,761 --> 00:08:54,199
I'M SO SORRY.
IF THERE'S ANYTHING I CAN DO...

116
00:08:54,232 --> 00:08:56,868
UH, COULD I TALK TO YOU
FOR A MINUTE?

117
00:08:56,902 --> 00:08:58,337
UM...SURE.

118
00:08:58,370 --> 00:09:01,073
OF COURSE.

119
00:08:58,370 --> 00:09:01,073
EXCUSE US?

120
00:08:58,370 --> 00:09:01,073
YEAH.

121
00:09:01,106 --> 00:09:03,576
SO, YOU WERE
SOLDIER'S PARTNER.

122
00:09:03,609 --> 00:09:04,743
THAT'S RIGHT.

123
00:09:04,776 --> 00:09:06,612
MIND IF I ASK YOU
A QUESTION?

124
00:09:06,645 --> 00:09:08,079
GO AHEAD.

125
00:09:09,314 --> 00:09:13,084
WHERE THE HELL WERE YOU
THE NIGHT MY BROTHER WAS KILLED?

126
00:09:13,118 --> 00:09:15,654
[ SIGHS ]
HE WAS SUSPENDED.

127
00:09:15,687 --> 00:09:18,691
HALF THE TIME HE WAS MY PARTNER,
HE WAS ON SUSPENSION.

128
00:09:18,724 --> 00:09:20,092
HOW...

129
00:09:25,330 --> 00:09:30,236
HOW WAS I TO KNOW
WHAT HE WAS...

130
00:09:32,704 --> 00:09:34,707
I'M SORRY.

131
00:09:34,740 --> 00:09:37,242
PLEASE UNDERSTAND, I'VE BEEN
A LITTLE UPSET LATELY.

132
00:09:37,275 --> 00:09:39,944
OH, IT'S...

133
00:09:39,978 --> 00:09:42,848
IT'S OKAY.
I FEEL THE SAME WAY.

134
00:09:42,881 --> 00:09:45,718
SOLDIER WAS LIKE
A BROTHER TO ME, TOO.

135
00:09:45,751 --> 00:09:48,254
YEAH,
THAT SOUNDS LIKE SOLDIER.

136
00:09:50,155 --> 00:09:52,625
DETECTIVE HAMPTON,
CAN YOU TELL ME WHAT HAPPENED?

137
00:09:52,658 --> 00:09:56,295
WELL...YOU KNOW ABOUT AS MUCH
AS WE DO RIGHT NOW.

138
00:09:56,328 --> 00:09:57,329
NO WITNESSES.

139
00:09:57,362 --> 00:09:59,264
PRELIMINARY
CORONER'S REPORT SAYS

140
00:09:59,297 --> 00:10:01,100
<i> THAT THERE WAS
 JUST ONE KILLER.</i>

141
00:10:01,133 --> 00:10:03,235
<i> AT LEAST SOLDIER TOOK
 THE MOTHER WITH HIM.</i>

142
00:10:03,268 --> 00:10:04,870
WHAT THE BLOODY HELL
WAS HE DOING

143
00:10:04,903 --> 00:10:07,073
IN AN ALLEY
IN CHINATOWN ANYWAY?

144
00:10:09,141 --> 00:10:11,142
CAN'T TALK HERE.

145
00:10:12,144 --> 00:10:13,779
OKAY.

146
00:10:13,812 --> 00:10:16,282
UH, HOW ABOUT WE GET TOGETHER
FOR SOME COFFEE LATER?

147
00:10:17,282 --> 00:10:19,952
I DON'T DO COFFEE.

148
00:10:19,985 --> 00:10:21,720
BAD FOR MY ULCER.

149
00:10:21,753 --> 00:10:23,322
[ CHUCKLES SOFTLY ]

150
00:10:24,823 --> 00:10:27,326
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS,
BLUES MUSIC PLAYING ]

151
00:10:31,730 --> 00:10:33,298
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

152
00:10:33,331 --> 00:10:35,300
AND BOURBON'S<i> GOOD</i>
FOR YOU ULCER?

153
00:10:35,333 --> 00:10:37,303
SCREW IT.
IT'S BEEN A CRAPPY DAY.

154
00:10:39,337 --> 00:10:41,306
SO, THE POLICE ARE LOOKING
INTO THIS, RIGHT?

155
00:10:41,339 --> 00:10:43,442
YEAH. OF COURSE.

156
00:10:43,475 --> 00:10:45,844
LISTEN, ERIC, I --

157
00:10:43,475 --> 00:10:45,844
HAWK.

158
00:10:45,877 --> 00:10:48,213
PRETTY MUCH EVERYONE
CALLS ME HAWK.

159
00:10:48,246 --> 00:10:49,247
NICKNAME.

160
00:10:49,281 --> 00:10:52,016
AND WHO DO YOU WATCH OVER?

161
00:10:52,050 --> 00:10:53,752
[ CHUCKLES ]

162
00:10:53,785 --> 00:10:56,188
RIGHT NOW, NO ONE.

163
00:10:59,257 --> 00:11:01,761
SO, YOU'RE AWARE
OF THE BA WONG GANG?

164
00:11:03,929 --> 00:11:05,164
WHAT'S THAT, AN ORGY?

165
00:11:05,197 --> 00:11:07,332
UH, NO.

166
00:11:07,365 --> 00:11:10,069
BA WONG IS A CHINATOWN GANG.

167
00:11:10,102 --> 00:11:12,271
THE RUTHLESS MASTERS.

168
00:11:12,304 --> 00:11:14,238
MOSTLY THEY PROTECT THEIR OWN

169
00:11:14,272 --> 00:11:16,275
FROM ALL THE OTHER GANGS
BREATHING DOWN THEIR NECKS,

170
00:11:16,308 --> 00:11:18,377
IN PARTICULAR,
THE DEATH SKULLS.

171
00:11:19,377 --> 00:11:20,846
DEATH SKULLS?

172
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:24,882
WOLF PACK. SKINHEADS.

173
00:11:24,916 --> 00:11:28,253
<i> FASCIST WHITE-SUPREMACIST
 BASTARDS. [ SIGHS ]</i>

174
00:11:28,286 --> 00:11:30,155
SOME OF THE BA WONG
HAVE GONE MISSING

175
00:11:30,188 --> 00:11:31,824
OVER THE PAST COUPLE
OF WEEKS.

176
00:11:31,857 --> 00:11:33,992
WE THINK THE SKINHEADS
ARE INVOLVED, BUT...

177
00:11:34,025 --> 00:11:35,294
[ MAN WOLF-WHISTLES ]

178
00:11:35,327 --> 00:11:37,229
OF COURSE,
NO ONE'S TALKING.

179
00:11:46,872 --> 00:11:49,742
AND, UH, WHAT'S THE DEAL
WITH THE SUSPENSION?

180
00:11:51,309 --> 00:11:53,245
SOLDIER HUNG
ONE OF THE SKINHEADS

181
00:11:53,278 --> 00:11:54,947
OUT OF A FIVE-STORY WINDOW,

182
00:11:54,980 --> 00:11:57,183
TRYING TO GET HIM TO TALK.

183
00:11:58,383 --> 00:12:00,753
SHOULD'VE FUCKING DROPPED HIM.

184
00:12:02,454 --> 00:12:04,356
[ PITCHER CLATTERS ]

185
00:12:11,997 --> 00:12:13,365
WILL YOU EXCUSE ME
A MINUTE, DETECTIVE?

186
00:12:13,398 --> 00:12:14,433
LIZZIE.

187
00:12:14,466 --> 00:12:16,301
EVERYONE CALLS ME LIZZIE.

188
00:12:16,334 --> 00:12:18,270
LIZZIE,
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

189
00:12:29,047 --> 00:12:31,751
GENTLEMEN, I COULDN'T HELP BUT
NOTICE YOU WERE SALUTING ME...

190
00:12:32,551 --> 00:12:35,387
AND UNDOUBTEDLY THINKING
OF CAUSING SOME TROUBLE.

191
00:12:35,420 --> 00:12:37,823
WELL, I JUST WANT TO ASSURE YOU
THAT IF YOU DO,

192
00:12:37,856 --> 00:12:40,125
I WILL LEAVE YOU CRIPPLED
AND TOOTHLESS.

193
00:12:40,158 --> 00:12:42,261
<i> NOW, I DON'T WANT TO RUIN
 EITHER OF OUR NIGHTS,</i>

194
00:12:42,294 --> 00:12:43,996
<i> SO WHY DON'T YOU JUST
 DO THE RIGHT THING?</i>

195
00:12:44,029 --> 00:12:47,333
HAVE A COUPLE OF COLD BEERS
AND CHILL OUT.

196
00:12:49,935 --> 00:12:50,868
<i> BARTENDER...</i>

197
00:12:50,902 --> 00:12:52,772
ANOTHER ROUND FOR THE BOYS.

198
00:12:59,077 --> 00:13:00,079
IT'S ON ME.

199
00:13:16,461 --> 00:13:18,297
I DON'T BELIEVE IT.

200
00:13:18,330 --> 00:13:20,966
UH, THAT WAS INCREDIBLE.

201
00:13:20,999 --> 00:13:23,869
YOUR BROTHER WOULD'VE
BEATEN THE SHIT OUT OF THEM.

202
00:13:23,902 --> 00:13:25,838
YEAH, WELL, I'VE HEARD
ABOUT HIS LEGAL BILLS.

203
00:13:26,638 --> 00:13:29,375
THEY LIKE TO SUE
HERE IN THE STATES.

204
00:13:33,178 --> 00:13:35,915
BARTENDER.
ANOTHER ROUND, PLEASE.

205
00:13:38,516 --> 00:13:41,219
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]
CAN I ASK YOU A QUESTION?

206
00:13:41,253 --> 00:13:43,055
YOU CAN ASK.

207
00:13:43,088 --> 00:13:44,522
ARE YOU MARRIED?

208
00:13:44,556 --> 00:13:45,958
DIVORCED.

209
00:13:45,991 --> 00:13:47,925
AND THE NEXT THING
YOU WANT TO KNOW IS,

210
00:13:47,959 --> 00:13:50,429
WAS THERE ANYTHING GOING ON
BETWEEN ME AND SOLDIER, RIGHT?

211
00:13:50,462 --> 00:13:51,630
YEAH.

212
00:13:51,663 --> 00:13:53,365
WELL,
EVERYBODY THOUGHT THAT.

213
00:13:53,398 --> 00:13:55,400
IF HE'D EVER JUST DROP
THE "LOVER BOY" BIT,

214
00:13:55,433 --> 00:13:57,336
I MIGHT HAVE
CONSIDERED IT.

215
00:13:57,369 --> 00:13:58,904
YOU SON OF A BITCH!

216
00:13:58,937 --> 00:14:00,072
Shit.

217
00:14:00,105 --> 00:14:03,475
I'LL TEACH YOU
TO EMBARRASS ME.

218
00:14:05,477 --> 00:14:07,246
JUST WAIT HERE.

219
00:14:09,414 --> 00:14:10,616
COME ON, FELLAS.

220
00:14:10,649 --> 00:14:12,551
WE'RE ALL FRIENDS HERE,
RIGHT?

221
00:14:16,054 --> 00:14:17,523
DAMN IT.

222
00:14:33,204 --> 00:14:37,108
I THOUGHT YOU SAID
YOU DIDN'T WANT LAWSUITS.

223
00:14:37,142 --> 00:14:39,044
NO WITNESSES.

224
00:14:46,384 --> 00:14:48,253
RIDE HOME?

225
00:14:48,286 --> 00:14:49,320
NO, THANKS.

226
00:14:49,354 --> 00:14:50,656
I FEEL LIKE WALKING.

227
00:14:50,689 --> 00:14:54,126
SURE.
WHERE CAN WE REACH YOU?

228
00:14:54,159 --> 00:14:55,394
NOW THE FUNERAL'S OVER,

229
00:14:55,427 --> 00:14:57,329
I'M GONNA CHECK OUT
OF THE HOTEL, SO, UH...

230
00:14:57,362 --> 00:14:59,531
ONCE I GET THE KEYS,
I'LL STAY AT SOLDIER'S AWHILE,

231
00:14:59,564 --> 00:15:02,401
JUST UNTIL I CAN GET
THINGS SQUARED AWAY.

232
00:15:02,434 --> 00:15:03,435
LISTEN...

233
00:15:04,703 --> 00:15:06,438
DON'T GO GETTING
ANY FUNNY IDEAS

234
00:15:06,471 --> 00:15:08,440
ABOUT CHECKING INTO
THIS MESS YOURSELF.

235
00:15:08,473 --> 00:15:10,608
<i> [ SIGHS ] ME?</i>

236
00:15:10,642 --> 00:15:12,444
NOW, WHY WOULD YOU SAY THAT?

237
00:15:13,445 --> 00:15:15,681
YOU'RE YOUR BROTHER'S
BROTHER.

238
00:16:23,381 --> 00:16:25,250
[ SIGHS SOFTLY ]

239
00:16:34,426 --> 00:16:36,061
<i> AAH!</i>

240
00:16:36,094 --> 00:16:37,296
[ GRUNTING ]

241
00:16:57,849 --> 00:16:59,451
AAH!

242
00:17:04,455 --> 00:17:06,591
[ PANTING ]

243
00:17:08,425 --> 00:17:11,463
I'M FINE, THANKS.
HOW ARE YOU?

244
00:17:44,195 --> 00:17:47,264
LOOKS LIKE WE FOUND YOUR
MISSING CHINESE GANG MEMBER.

245
00:17:47,298 --> 00:17:50,102
70-YEAR-OLD WOMAN ON A CHARTER
REELED IN THE BODY.

246
00:17:50,135 --> 00:17:52,337
NEEDLESS TO SAY,
SHE WON THE POOL. [ LAUGHS ]

247
00:17:52,370 --> 00:17:53,472
GOT AN I.D.?

248
00:17:53,505 --> 00:17:56,708
NO, NOT YET.
ASIAN. 5'9", 150.

249
00:18:01,446 --> 00:18:02,581
DOC...

250
00:18:02,614 --> 00:18:04,583
DOC SATTLER,
DETECTIVE HAMPTON.

251
00:18:04,616 --> 00:18:06,751
DOCTOR.

252
00:18:06,784 --> 00:18:08,253
PLEASURE, DETECTIVE.

253
00:18:08,286 --> 00:18:09,855
CARE FOR A LOOK
AT THE CATCH OF THE DAY?

254
00:18:09,888 --> 00:18:11,156
I SUPPOSE.

255
00:18:12,557 --> 00:18:13,725
OH.

256
00:18:13,758 --> 00:18:17,796
SORRY, I FORGOT.
I MOVED THINGS AROUND A BIT.

257
00:18:17,829 --> 00:18:19,898
THIS GUY WAS DRAWN,
QUARTERED,

258
00:18:19,931 --> 00:18:24,269
AND NEATLY PACKAGED
IN A COMPACT LITTLE BUNDLE.

259
00:18:24,302 --> 00:18:25,803
THEY MUST HAVE
WEIGHTED HIM DOWN,

260
00:18:25,837 --> 00:18:27,873
BUT SOMEHOW
HIS BODY GOT LOOSE.

261
00:18:27,906 --> 00:18:29,407
LOOK AT HIS GUT.

262
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:33,112
SHARK SMORGASBORD.
ORGANS ALL GONE.

263
00:18:38,516 --> 00:18:40,452
BA WONG TATTOO.

264
00:18:48,226 --> 00:18:50,896
LOOK, FIRST OF ALL...

265
00:18:50,929 --> 00:18:52,430
TELL ME WHO YOU ARE

266
00:18:52,463 --> 00:18:54,299
AND WHAT THE HELL
YOU'RE DOING HERE.

267
00:18:54,332 --> 00:18:56,835
HEY, SCREW YOU, MAN.
I LIVE HERE.

268
00:18:56,868 --> 00:18:58,537
COME AGAIN?

269
00:18:59,938 --> 00:19:02,440
OKAY, I DON'T
REALLY LIVE HERE.

270
00:19:02,473 --> 00:19:05,177
BUT SOLDIER WAS LETTING ME
CRASH FOR A WHILE, MAN.

271
00:19:05,210 --> 00:19:07,579
<i> WHO THE FUCK ARE YOU,
 ANYWAY?</i>

272
00:19:07,612 --> 00:19:09,414
I'M HIS STEPBROTHER.

273
00:19:09,447 --> 00:19:11,649
OH.

274
00:19:11,683 --> 00:19:13,519
YOU'RE THE GUY
IN THE PICTURE.

275
00:19:16,921 --> 00:19:18,157
I'M SORRY.

276
00:19:27,365 --> 00:19:28,400
[ SIGHS ]

277
00:19:28,433 --> 00:19:30,469
SO, HOW DO YOU KNOW SOLDIER?

278
00:19:31,436 --> 00:19:33,338
[ SIGHS ]

279
00:19:33,371 --> 00:19:35,473
MY BROTHER.

280
00:19:35,506 --> 00:19:37,475
LIPING.

281
00:19:37,508 --> 00:19:39,344
THEY GRABBED HIM, MAN.

282
00:19:39,377 --> 00:19:41,379
FUCKING SKINHEADS.

283
00:19:41,412 --> 00:19:42,948
<i> ABOUT A WEEK AGO.</i>

284
00:19:42,981 --> 00:19:45,283
<i> HE TOLD US
 NOT TO TALK TO THE COPS.</i>

285
00:19:45,316 --> 00:19:47,319
BUT I KNEW SOLDIER WAS COOL.

286
00:19:47,352 --> 00:19:49,955
SO I FILLED HIM IN.

287
00:19:49,988 --> 00:19:52,491
HE WAS LETTING ME CRASH
WHILE HE CHECKED THINGS OUT.

288
00:19:53,458 --> 00:19:54,459
<i> HEY, MAN...</i>

289
00:19:54,492 --> 00:19:57,229
HOW ABOUT UNTYING ME?

290
00:19:57,262 --> 00:19:58,664
[ SIGHS ]

291
00:20:09,407 --> 00:20:10,708
[ GROANS ]

292
00:20:17,515 --> 00:20:18,951
SO, WHAT'S YOUR NAME?

293
00:20:19,917 --> 00:20:22,788
LIPO. LIPO CHUNG.

294
00:20:24,422 --> 00:20:25,424
NAME'S HAWK.

295
00:20:26,557 --> 00:20:27,459
HAWK.

296
00:20:35,967 --> 00:20:37,235
YOU FIGHT PRETTY GOOD.

297
00:20:37,269 --> 00:20:40,472
YOU'RE JUST LUCKY
YOU DIDN'T PULL ANY OF
THAT KUNG-FU SHIT ON ME.

298
00:20:41,472 --> 00:20:42,407
HEY...

299
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:44,776
THAT'S A RACIST STATEMENT,
MAN.

300
00:20:44,809 --> 00:20:46,845
JUST 'CAUSE I'M ASIAN,
I KNOW KUNG FU?

301
00:20:46,878 --> 00:20:49,481
<i> YOU THINK, LIKE, EVERY FUCKING
 CHINESE GUY IN THE WORLD</i>

302
00:20:49,514 --> 00:20:50,681
<i> IS LIKE BRUCE LEE, RIGHT?</i>

303
00:20:50,715 --> 00:20:53,451
AH-SO! OH!

304
00:20:53,484 --> 00:20:56,321
OKAY, I'M SORRY, ALL RIGHT?
I DIDN'T MEAN ANYTHING BY IT.

305
00:20:57,689 --> 00:21:00,459
I'M JUST
RAGGING ON YOU, MAN.

306
00:21:02,627 --> 00:21:05,996
LISTEN, I'M THINKING
OF CHECKING INTO
SOLDIER'S DEATH MYSELF.

307
00:21:06,030 --> 00:21:09,533
<i> COULD YOU, UH,
 TAKE ME TO YOUR LEADE?</i>

308
00:21:09,567 --> 00:21:10,869
YOON?

309
00:21:10,902 --> 00:21:14,439
[ CHUCKLES ]
HE'LL EAT YOU ALIVE, ROUND-EYE.

310
00:21:14,472 --> 00:21:16,374
[ CHUCKLES ]

311
00:21:16,407 --> 00:21:18,577
DON'T BE
CALLING ME THAT, OKAY?

312
00:21:20,978 --> 00:21:23,415
[ LAUGHS ]

313
00:21:23,448 --> 00:21:24,916
HEH.

314
00:21:35,860 --> 00:21:36,861
[ GRUNTS ]

315
00:21:48,740 --> 00:21:49,774
REPORT.

316
00:21:49,807 --> 00:21:51,710
NOT A GOOD WEEK.

317
00:21:51,743 --> 00:21:55,379
OUTCALL, NUMBERS,
AND MUNITIONS ALL TOOK HITS.

318
00:21:55,413 --> 00:21:58,516
<i> THE FRONT STREET MERCHANTS
 ARE ORGANIZING AGAINST
 THE PROTECTION MONEY.</i>

319
00:21:58,549 --> 00:22:00,352
<i> JOJO'S HEADING DOWN
 WITH A BASEBALL BAT</i>

320
00:22:00,385 --> 00:22:01,786
<i> TO IMPRESS THEM
 WITH OUR POINT OF VIEW.</i>

321
00:22:01,819 --> 00:22:04,456
THEY GOT A NEW CAPTAIN
DOWN AT THE 63rd.

322
00:22:04,489 --> 00:22:06,725
<i> LOOKS LIKE A REAL GO-GETTER.
 TOUGH NUT TO CRACK.</i>

323
00:22:16,401 --> 00:22:17,736
<i> TOOK A HEAVY HIT
 ON NUMBERS.</i>

324
00:22:17,769 --> 00:22:19,771
<i> 7 AND 13 BOTH CAME UP.</i>

325
00:22:19,804 --> 00:22:22,374
<i> WE LOST 80,
 MAYBE 90 GRAND.</i>

326
00:22:22,407 --> 00:22:25,810
<i> BUT THE ROBBERY
 AT AL'S GUN SHOP
 WENT WITHOUT A HITCH.</i>

327
00:22:25,843 --> 00:22:26,845
AAH!

328
00:22:35,486 --> 00:22:39,057
AND BIO? FORGET IT.
WE'VE YET TO SHOW A PROFIT.

329
00:22:39,090 --> 00:22:41,793
<i> THE COSTS OF RUNNING THE
 OPERATION ARE OUT OF CONTROL.</i>

330
00:22:41,826 --> 00:22:44,496
<i> EQUIPMENT, MAINTENANCE,
 PERSONNEL --</i>

331
00:22:44,529 --> 00:22:45,964
<i> GOING THROUGH THE ROOF.</i>

332
00:22:45,997 --> 00:22:48,066
<i> AND BUSINESS IS SLOW.</i>

333
00:22:48,866 --> 00:22:50,569
AAH!

334
00:22:48,866 --> 00:22:50,569
AAH!

335
00:22:52,203 --> 00:22:55,507
WHAT AM I DOING THIS FOR,
MY HEALTH?

336
00:22:55,540 --> 00:22:58,009
[ SIGHS ]

337
00:22:58,042 --> 00:23:01,478
<i> Duquesne: Excuse me, Mr. Gar.
 Mr. Siegel's here.</i>

338
00:23:01,512 --> 00:23:03,114
SEND HIM RIGHT UP.

339
00:23:03,147 --> 00:23:05,484
<i> Right away, sir.</i>

340
00:23:07,185 --> 00:23:09,421
I GOT A FEELING
THIS SIEGEL

341
00:23:09,454 --> 00:23:12,456
COULD TURN THIS BIO THING
AROUND FOR US.

342
00:23:12,490 --> 00:23:15,160
THIS COULD BE
A REAL OPPORTUNITY, BLADE.

343
00:23:15,193 --> 00:23:18,496
SIEGEL CONTROLS
THE SOUTHEAST.

344
00:23:18,529 --> 00:23:21,533
IN MIAMI,
THEY CALL HIM THE KING.

345
00:23:21,566 --> 00:23:23,435
THE KING OF CRIME.

346
00:23:25,837 --> 00:23:27,439
[ SIGHS ]

347
00:23:27,472 --> 00:23:30,742
HE CAN HELP US ALL RIGHT,
BLADE.

348
00:23:30,775 --> 00:23:32,744
BUT REMEMBER...

349
00:23:32,777 --> 00:23:35,147
WE SCREW UP
WITH SIEGEL...

350
00:23:39,050 --> 00:23:41,886
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

351
00:23:41,919 --> 00:23:44,489
COME IN.

352
00:23:41,919 --> 00:23:44,489
[ DOOR OPENS ]

353
00:23:46,123 --> 00:23:47,492
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

354
00:23:55,533 --> 00:23:58,136
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.

355
00:23:58,169 --> 00:24:00,972
[ COUGHING ]

356
00:24:01,005 --> 00:24:03,141
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

357
00:24:03,174 --> 00:24:06,077
THE WORD IS
THAT YOU CAN HELP ME.

358
00:24:09,814 --> 00:24:12,584
IT WOULD BE AN HONOR,
MR. SIEGEL.

359
00:24:12,617 --> 00:24:15,486
BUT ACCORDING TO THIS,
YOU'RE ONE RARE BIRD.

360
00:24:15,520 --> 00:24:18,990
I'LL GIVE YOU $1 MILLION.

361
00:24:19,023 --> 00:24:22,526
I'M WORTH A MILLION DOLLARS,
AIN'T I, SWEETIE?

362
00:24:22,560 --> 00:24:24,796
[ CHUCKLES ]

363
00:24:24,829 --> 00:24:26,630
HUNDRED THOU DOWN.

364
00:24:26,664 --> 00:24:29,533
<i> YOU HAVE THE MERCHANDISE
 FOR ME WITHIN A WEEK.</i>

365
00:24:29,567 --> 00:24:30,902
YOU DON'T DELIVER,

366
00:24:30,935 --> 00:24:33,271
YOU WON'T NEED MONEY
WHERE YOU'LL BE GOING.

367
00:24:33,304 --> 00:24:34,973
[ CHUCKLES ]

368
00:24:35,006 --> 00:24:37,842
SO...DEAL?

369
00:24:37,875 --> 00:24:40,178
DEAL.

370
00:24:42,213 --> 00:24:44,616
NO, DON'T FUCKING TOUCH ME.

371
00:24:44,649 --> 00:24:46,684
I DON'T KNOW WHERE YOU BEEN.

372
00:24:46,717 --> 00:24:50,555
THE LAST THING I NEED IS
A GODDAMN VIRUS OR SOMETHING.

373
00:24:50,588 --> 00:24:52,690
DUQUESNE, ESCORT OUR GUEST
TO THE OFFICE,

374
00:24:52,723 --> 00:24:55,293
AND, UH, WE'LL ARRANGE
HIS AGREEMENT.

375
00:24:55,326 --> 00:24:57,562
YES, SIR, MR. GARR.

376
00:25:08,940 --> 00:25:10,909
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

377
00:25:14,345 --> 00:25:16,314
GET CLAY ON THE LINE.

378
00:25:16,347 --> 00:25:18,917
WE'RE GONNA NEED
A FEW MORE ROUNDUPS.

379
00:25:18,950 --> 00:25:20,652
YES, SIR.

380
00:25:22,219 --> 00:25:25,023
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS,
LAUGHTER ]

381
00:25:32,697 --> 00:25:34,998
SO, YOU'RE
THE COP'S BROTHER, HUH?

382
00:25:35,032 --> 00:25:36,568
YOU LOOK LIKE HIM.

383
00:25:36,601 --> 00:25:39,905
BUT, THEN, ALL YOU ROUND-EYES
LOOK ALIKE TO ME.

384
00:25:42,073 --> 00:25:47,045
SO, YOON, WHAT CAN YOU TELL ME
ABOUT THE DEATH SKULLS?

385
00:25:47,078 --> 00:25:50,682
FUCKERS ARE ON
THE WARPATH, MAN.

386
00:25:50,715 --> 00:25:52,350
THEY GOT THESE GUNS --

387
00:25:52,383 --> 00:25:55,253
LIKE BEING CLOCKED
BY TYSON -- BAM!

388
00:25:55,286 --> 00:25:57,622
KNOCK YOU DOWN...

389
00:25:57,655 --> 00:26:00,058
BUT DON'T KILL YOU.

390
00:26:00,091 --> 00:26:04,696
THEN WHEN YOU'RE STUNNED,
THEY KIDNAP YOUR ASS.

391
00:26:04,729 --> 00:26:05,830
WHY?

392
00:26:05,863 --> 00:26:07,999
MAN, IF I KNEW THAT...

393
00:26:08,032 --> 00:26:10,134
BUT I'LL TELL YOU THIS --

394
00:26:10,167 --> 00:26:14,138
THOSE BALD SON OF A BITCHES
ARE GOING DOWN.

395
00:26:14,171 --> 00:26:16,975
I JUST FOUND OUT
WHERE THEIR NEW DEN IS.

396
00:26:22,313 --> 00:26:24,149
[ WOMEN SCREAMING ]

397
00:26:27,652 --> 00:26:28,753
IT'S KHAN!

398
00:26:34,358 --> 00:26:37,794
BROAD FUCKING DAYLIGHT!

399
00:26:37,828 --> 00:26:39,163
THAT DOES IT.

400
00:26:39,196 --> 00:26:41,331
EVERY ONE OF THOSE BASTARDS
ARE GONNA BURN TONIGHT.

401
00:26:41,365 --> 00:26:43,067
HOLD ON A SECOND, YOON.

402
00:26:43,100 --> 00:26:45,235
LOOK, I KNOW YOU'RE UPSET,
BUT IF YOU GO CHARGING IN THERE,

403
00:26:45,269 --> 00:26:46,637
A LOT OF PEOPLE
ARE GONNA GET KILLED,

404
00:26:46,671 --> 00:26:49,941
AND YOU'RE NOT GONNA BE
ANY CLOSER TO FINDING OUT
WHAT'S GOING ON

405
00:26:49,974 --> 00:26:52,210
OR WHAT'S HAPPENED
TO YOUR MISSING BOYS.

406
00:26:52,243 --> 00:26:54,646
YOU GOT
ANY BETTER IDEAS?

407
00:26:54,679 --> 00:26:55,980
[ WOMEN WHIMPERING ]

408
00:26:56,013 --> 00:26:57,282
YEAH.

409
00:27:06,757 --> 00:27:08,960
THIS IS SOLDIER'S GEAR.

410
00:27:10,895 --> 00:27:13,764
THERE MUST BE
SOMETHING HERE WE CAN USE.

411
00:27:15,399 --> 00:27:17,101
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

412
00:28:00,377 --> 00:28:01,312
NOW WHAT, ROUND-EYE?

413
00:28:01,345 --> 00:28:03,281
WE'LL GO TO
THE DEATH SKULLS' HEADQUARTERS

414
00:28:03,314 --> 00:28:05,183
AND FIND OUT
WHERE YOUR BOYS ARE.

415
00:28:06,183 --> 00:28:09,054
DO YOU KNOW
A GOOD COSTUME SHOP?

416
00:28:27,938 --> 00:28:29,440
WHERE DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE GOING?

417
00:28:29,473 --> 00:28:31,242
I'M GOING WITH YOU.

418
00:28:31,275 --> 00:28:34,312
I THINK THEY MIGHT SMELL
A RAT, SLANT-EYE.

419
00:28:34,345 --> 00:28:37,215
KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

420
00:28:37,248 --> 00:28:40,284
YOU HOLD ON TO THIS
JUST IN CASE.

421
00:28:40,317 --> 00:28:41,919
MAN, THIS IS STUPID.

422
00:28:41,952 --> 00:28:43,454
THERE'S NO WAY
THEY'RE GONNA LET YOU IN.

423
00:28:43,487 --> 00:28:45,323
WOULD YOU RELAX?

424
00:28:45,356 --> 00:28:48,259
JUST WATCH.
YOU MIGHT LEARN SOMETHING.

425
00:28:50,294 --> 00:28:53,431
IF I'M NOT BACK IN TEN MINUTES,
THEN CALL THE POLICE.

426
00:29:14,051 --> 00:29:15,453
FUCK YOU WANT?

427
00:29:16,954 --> 00:29:18,523
FIRE INSPECTOR.

428
00:29:18,556 --> 00:29:20,992
WE DON'T GOT NO FIRES
TO INSPECT.

429
00:29:21,025 --> 00:29:23,061
TAKE A FUCKING HIKE!

430
00:29:25,563 --> 00:29:29,033
I SAID GET LOST!

431
00:29:29,066 --> 00:29:30,334
<i> LISTEN UP, BALDY...</i>

432
00:29:30,367 --> 00:29:32,336
I DON'T THINK
YOU QUITE UNDERSTAND.

433
00:29:32,369 --> 00:29:33,971
YOU CAN LET ME IN NOW,

434
00:29:34,004 --> 00:29:36,841
OR I CAN COME BACK IN AN HOUR
WITH A POLICE ESCORT.

435
00:29:36,874 --> 00:29:39,911
<i> TAKES FIVE MINUTES
 TO CHECK YOUR SMOKE DETECTORS.</i>

436
00:29:39,944 --> 00:29:42,280
SO WHY DON'T YOU
OPEN UP THE DOOR?

437
00:29:59,430 --> 00:30:01,132
FIRE INSPECTOR.

438
00:30:01,165 --> 00:30:03,935
<i> WHAT A FUCKING JOKE.</i>

439
00:30:06,437 --> 00:30:07,572
[ MEN COUGHING ]

440
00:30:16,013 --> 00:30:19,884
<i> NOW DOES SOMEBODY
 WANT TO SHOW ME WHERE
 THE SMOKE DETECTOR IS?</i>

441
00:30:21,151 --> 00:30:23,254
SHOW HIM, ELWIN.

442
00:30:23,287 --> 00:30:24,355
<i> YEAH...</i>

443
00:30:24,388 --> 00:30:26,224
SHOW ME, ELWIN.

444
00:30:48,112 --> 00:30:50,181
[ SIGHS ]
NOW, NOW, ELWIN.

445
00:30:50,214 --> 00:30:51,416
THIS JUST WON'T DO.

446
00:31:39,196 --> 00:31:42,166
<i> NOW, THAT WASN'T SO BAD,
 WAS IT, FELLAS?</i>

447
00:31:42,199 --> 00:31:44,435
SEE HOW EASY IT IS
TO COOPERATE WITH THE LAW?

448
00:31:44,468 --> 00:31:49,140
HOLD IT RIGHT THERE,
YOU SMUG ASSWIPE.

449
00:31:54,411 --> 00:31:56,380
PRETTY SMOOTH, HUH?

450
00:31:56,413 --> 00:31:58,349
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT...

451
00:32:03,520 --> 00:32:06,691
IT'S ON ME, FELLAS.

452
00:32:06,724 --> 00:32:08,359
HELP YOURSELF.

453
00:32:10,327 --> 00:32:12,130
YOU ALL HAVE A NICE DAY.

454
00:32:19,403 --> 00:32:21,405
I DON'T BELIEVE IT.

455
00:32:21,438 --> 00:32:23,374
I DON'T
FUCKING BELIEVE IT.

456
00:32:23,407 --> 00:32:27,078
YOU JUST WALKED IN,
THEN WALKED OUT.

457
00:32:27,111 --> 00:32:29,213
[ LAUGHS ]

458
00:32:29,246 --> 00:32:31,349
STAND BY.

459
00:32:36,453 --> 00:32:38,990
[ COUGHING ]

460
00:32:39,023 --> 00:32:41,024
[ LAUGHTER ]

461
00:32:44,528 --> 00:32:46,030
[ BEEPING ]

462
00:32:51,368 --> 00:32:53,370
LOOK OVER HERE.
CHECK IT OUT.

463
00:32:51,368 --> 00:32:53,370
WHAT IS IT?

464
00:32:53,404 --> 00:32:55,406
<i> WHAT'S GOING ON, MA?</i>

465
00:32:55,439 --> 00:32:57,575
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

466
00:32:58,442 --> 00:32:59,711
<i> HEY!</i>

467
00:32:58,442 --> 00:32:59,711
<i> OH!</i>

468
00:33:05,282 --> 00:33:06,985
[ MUFFLED BREATHING ]

469
00:33:10,521 --> 00:33:12,255
YOU READY?

470
00:33:37,448 --> 00:33:38,750
AMAZING.

471
00:33:39,716 --> 00:33:42,386
WHAT IF THEY DIDN'T
GO FOR THE CIGARS?

472
00:33:42,419 --> 00:33:45,456
PUT ON A 10-MINUTE TIMER,
JUST IN CASE.

473
00:33:46,457 --> 00:33:48,593
<i> NOW, LET'S FIND YOUR MATES.</i>

474
00:33:57,334 --> 00:33:59,170
[ CAN CLATTERS ]

475
00:34:10,280 --> 00:34:11,282
HEY.

476
00:34:16,152 --> 00:34:18,188
CLAY.
THAT'S THEIR LEADER.

477
00:34:18,222 --> 00:34:19,257
THAT'S HIS BAND.

478
00:34:19,290 --> 00:34:23,360
<i> GRINDING, HIGH-SPEED,
 INDUSTRIAL HATE MUSIC.</i>

479
00:34:23,393 --> 00:34:25,329
<i> DELIGHTFUL SHIT.</i>

480
00:34:25,362 --> 00:34:27,764
