00:41:04,794 --> 00:41:06,263
<i> 4...5...</i>

584
00:41:06,296 --> 00:41:09,265
COME ON! MOVE IT!

585
00:41:06,296 --> 00:41:09,265
<i> 6...7...8...</i>

586
00:41:09,299 --> 00:41:11,768
