I DON'T CARE IF IT TAKES YOU
20 MORE TRIES

955
01:00:55,384 --> 01:00:56,686
OR 20 MORE FINGERS.

956
01:00:56,719 --> 01:00:58,954
I WANT HIM DEAD.

957
01:00:58,987 --> 01:01:00,657
YOU GOT IT?

958
01:01:07,129 --> 01:01:09,298
[ GRUNTS, GROANS ]

959
01:01:14,103 --> 01:01:18,374
DO YOU AND THAT CRANIUM-IMPAIRED
IDIOT CATCH MY DRIFT?

960
01:01:23,512 --> 01:01:28,217
ON SECOND THOUGHT,
WE NEED THE BODIES.

961
01:01:28,250 --> 01:01:32,955
WE DON'T HAVE THE SKINHEADS
TO DO THE ROUNDUPS ANYMORE.

962
01:01:32,988 --> 01:01:35,790
EXTRA CREDIT
IF YOU YO-YOS BAG HIM ALIVE.

963
01:01:35,824 --> 01:01:37,994
BRING HIM BACK HERE.

964
01:01:44,299 --> 01:01:47,269
SO, WHAT'S WITH
THE NICKNAME -- HAWK?

965
01:01:47,302 --> 01:01:49,939
JUST A SWIFT-SWOOPING,
KILLER TYPE OF GUY?

966
01:01:49,972 --> 01:01:51,407
WHAT?
[ CHUCKLES ]

967
01:01:51,440 --> 01:01:54,243
IN A DEFENSIVE SENSE, PERHAPS.

968
01:01:55,911 --> 01:01:57,947
AND HOW ABOUT YOU
AND JACK?

969
01:01:57,980 --> 01:02:00,449
HE WAS AS AMERICAN AS APPLE PIE,
AND YOU'RE...

970
01:02:00,482 --> 01:02:02,418
A LOYAL SUBJECT
OF THE QUEEN.

971
01:02:02,451 --> 01:02:04,954
YEAH.
SO HOW'D THAT HAPPEN?

972
01:02:06,155 --> 01:02:07,757
[ SIGHS ]

973
01:02:07,790 --> 01:02:10,993
MY DAD WAS IN THE MARINES --
U.S. MARINES.

974
01:02:11,026 --> 01:02:13,229
HE'D MOVE FROM STATION
TO STATION.

975
01:02:13,262 --> 01:02:17,199
<i> JACK'S MOTHER DIED WHEN HE
 WAS FOUR YEARS OLD IN AFRICA.</i>

976
01:02:17,232 --> 01:02:18,868
DAD REMARRIED IN ENGLAND

977
01:02:18,901 --> 01:02:21,337
WHEN HE WAS STATIONED
AT THE U.S. EMBASSY IN LONDON.

978
01:02:21,370 --> 01:02:23,105
AND THAT WAS YOUR MOM?

979
01:02:23,138 --> 01:02:24,073
<i> YEAH.</i>

980
01:02:24,106 --> 01:02:26,075
<i> WE KNOCKED AROUND THE WORLD
 FOR A WHILE</i>

981
01:02:26,108 --> 01:02:27,943
UNTIL DAD WAS SENT
TO VIETNAM.

982
01:02:27,976 --> 01:02:30,246
<i> HE WAS KILLED PROTECTING
 THE U.S. EMBASSY</i>

983
01:02:30,279 --> 01:02:32,348
<i> IN THE FINAL DAYS
 OF THE EVACUATION.</i>

984
01:02:32,381 --> 01:02:35,484
OH.
TALK ABOUT YOUR BAD BREAKS.

985
01:02:36,418 --> 01:02:38,053
WE LIVED IN AMERICA
FOR A WHILE

986
01:02:38,086 --> 01:02:40,356
UNTIL MUM DECIDED TO RETURN
TO ENGLAND.

987
01:02:40,389 --> 01:02:42,224
JACK DIDN'T WANT TO GO.

988
01:02:42,257 --> 01:02:44,927
HE WAS 17 AND DECIDED TO JOIN
THE MARINES.

989
01:02:46,295 --> 01:02:48,097
AND WHEN YOU FINISHED SCHOOL,

990
01:02:48,130 --> 01:02:51,467
YOU JOINED THE BRITISH MARINES,
JUST LIKE YOUR BROTHER.

991
01:02:51,500 --> 01:02:52,968
[ CHUCKLES SOFTLY ]

992
01:02:53,001 --> 01:02:55,171
JACK WAS MY HERO.

993
01:02:56,238 --> 01:02:59,442
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

994
01:03:22,431 --> 01:03:26,569
SO, UH, HOW ABOUT
COMING BACK TO MY PLACE?

995
01:03:27,936 --> 01:03:30,206
HOW ABOUT MY PLACE?

996
01:03:30,239 --> 01:03:32,274
OH, SHIT.

997
01:03:32,307 --> 01:03:36,111
I LIVE IN CAMDEN PARK.
IT'S A HALF-AN-HOUR DRIVE.

998
01:03:38,013 --> 01:03:40,049
SO IT'S MY PLACE.

999
01:03:40,082 --> 01:03:41,383
DAMN!

1000
01:03:41,416 --> 01:03:43,853
IT'S STILL A MESS.

1001
01:03:44,386 --> 01:03:47,423
MMM.
MY PLACE IT IS.

1002
01:03:48,924 --> 01:03:51,227
<i> MY</i> PLACE.

1003
01:03:51,260 --> 01:03:52,328
<i> HMM.</i>

1004
01:03:52,361 --> 01:03:54,330
<i> Both:
 HOW ABOUT RIGHT HERE?</i>

1005
01:04:32,634 --> 01:04:35,171
WE'RE HERE
FOR THE NEW ARRIVAL.

1006
01:04:36,204 --> 01:04:39,141
YOU WANT HIM,
YOU GO THROUGH ME.

1007
01:04:39,174 --> 01:04:40,309
[ GUN COCKS ]

1008
01:04:40,342 --> 01:04:41,310
WHATEVER.

1009
01:04:41,343 --> 01:04:42,310
NO.

1010
01:04:43,412 --> 01:04:45,314
LIPING, IT'S ALL RIGHT.

1011
01:04:45,347 --> 01:04:47,183
<i> MOVE IT.</i>

1012
01:04:55,324 --> 01:04:57,026
[ LATCH CLICKS ]

1013
01:05:05,300 --> 01:05:08,304
[ MACHINERY BEEPING ]

1014
01:05:20,515 --> 01:05:21,517
SAW.

1015
01:05:26,455 --> 01:05:28,457
MORELLI,
YOU'RE REPLACING JOHNNY.

1016
01:05:28,490 --> 01:05:30,158
I WANT YOU ON STANDBY.

1017
01:05:30,192 --> 01:05:31,627
YOU'VE GOT AN 8:00 A.M. FLIGHT
TO LIBYA.

1018
01:05:31,660 --> 01:05:33,729
H-HEY, WAIT.
I-I'M NO DELIVERYMAN.

1019
01:05:33,762 --> 01:05:35,531
UH, C-CAN'T YOU GET
SOMEBODY ELSE?

1020
01:05:35,564 --> 01:05:36,665
THERE IS NO ONE ELSE.

1021
01:05:36,698 --> 01:05:39,702
[ SAW GRINDING ]

1022
01:05:43,372 --> 01:05:46,274
PINKUS, I WANT YOU STICKING
AROUND TILL AFTER CLEANUP.

1023
01:05:46,308 --> 01:05:47,643
YOU'RE ON
PACKAGE-DISPOSAL DUTY.

1024
01:05:47,676 --> 01:05:50,045
BENIGNI IS WAITING TO TAKE YOU
OUT TO PIER 91.

1025
01:05:50,078 --> 01:05:51,346
YOU GOT IT, BLADE.

1026
01:05:51,380 --> 01:05:53,649
WHOA.
LOOKY HERE.

1027
01:05:55,650 --> 01:05:59,322
CONGRATULATIONS.
IT'S A HEART.

1028
01:06:09,331 --> 01:06:10,499
[ HISSES ]

1029
01:06:12,501 --> 01:06:14,337
[ COOLER LID CLOSES ]

1030
01:06:15,704 --> 01:06:19,175
YOU GUYS EVER WATCH THE DOC
MAKE ONE OF HER PACKAGES?

1031
01:06:20,542 --> 01:06:24,480
[ SAW BUZZING ]

1032
01:06:30,318 --> 01:06:33,122
AND POLICE HAVE IDENTIFIED
THE VICTIM OF THAT FIRE

1033
01:06:33,155 --> 01:06:34,190
<i> AS GERALD CLAY,</i>

1034
01:06:34,223 --> 01:06:37,092
<i> SUSPECTED LEADER
 OF THE NOTORIOUS SKINHEAD GANG</i>

1035
01:06:37,125 --> 01:06:38,594
KNOWN AS THE DEATH SKULLS.

1036
01:06:38,627 --> 01:06:40,529
<i> CLAY'S CHARRED REMAINS
 WERE FIRST DISCOVERED</i>

1037
01:06:40,562 --> 01:06:43,464
<i> BY FIRE FIGHTERS
 RESPONDING TO A 911 CALL</i>

1038
01:06:43,498 --> 01:06:45,467
IN THE GREENPOINT SECTION.

1039
01:06:45,500 --> 01:06:46,435
WAIT. GO BACK.
WHAT WAS THAT?

1040
01:06:46,468 --> 01:06:48,604
WHO THE HELL
ARE YOU TALKIN' ABOUT?

1041
01:06:46,468 --> 01:06:48,604
NOTHING.

1042
01:06:48,637 --> 01:06:50,672
COULD YOU JUST GO BACK?
I WANT TO SEE THAT.

1043
01:06:50,705 --> 01:06:53,142
LIZ, IT'S JUST AN OLD
BLACK-AND-WHITE MOVIE.

1044
01:06:53,175 --> 01:06:54,276
IT'S NOTHING.

1045
01:06:53,175 --> 01:06:54,276
<i> HAWK...</i>

1046
01:06:54,309 --> 01:06:55,411
WHAT'S THE MATTER
WITH YOU?

1047
01:06:54,309 --> 01:06:55,411
WHAT?

1048
01:06:55,444 --> 01:06:56,345
COME ON!

1049
01:06:56,378 --> 01:06:57,346
GIVE IT TO ME.

1050
01:06:56,378 --> 01:06:57,346
LIZZIE.

1051
01:06:57,379 --> 01:06:59,348
NOW...
WHAT CHANNEL WAS IT?

1052
01:06:59,381 --> 01:07:03,452
IT WAS NOTHING! IT...
[ SIGHS ] SEE?

1053
01:07:03,485 --> 01:07:06,321
FIRE INVESTIGATORS BELIEVE
THAT CLAY WAS BURNED TO DEATH

1054
01:07:03,485 --> 01:07:06,321
HERE.

1055
01:07:06,354 --> 01:07:08,323
IN A HOMEMADE NAPALM BLAST.

1056
01:07:08,356 --> 01:07:11,827
<i> EARLIER TODAY,
 WE SPOKE WITH CHIEF
 INVESTIGATOR MORRIS SHERWIN.</i>

1057
01:07:11,860 --> 01:07:14,229
MY GUESS IS THAT THIS IS
THE WORK OF A SPECIALIST,

1058
01:07:14,262 --> 01:07:16,465
SOMEONE WITH HEAVY-DUTY
GUERRILLA TRAINING

1059
01:07:16,498 --> 01:07:18,133
OR MAYBE SPECIAL FORCES.

1060
01:07:18,166 --> 01:07:21,136
WE'LL KNOW MORE IN A FEW DAYS
AFTER WE'VE HAD OCCASION --

1061
01:07:21,169 --> 01:07:23,439
YOU LYING PIECE OF SHIT!

1062
01:07:23,472 --> 01:07:25,107
HOW COULD YOU DO THIS?

1063
01:07:25,140 --> 01:07:27,442
LIZZIE, I'M SORRY.
I CAN EXPLAIN.

1064
01:07:27,476 --> 01:07:28,410
YEAH? YEAH?
WELL, GO AHEAD.

1065
01:07:28,443 --> 01:07:30,279
EXPLAIN.
I WANT TO HEAR THIS.

1066
01:07:30,312 --> 01:07:32,147
[ SIGHS ]

1067
01:07:34,883 --> 01:07:37,218
OKAY,
MAYBE I CAN'T EXPLAIN.

1068
01:07:37,252 --> 01:07:40,255
OH, JESUS, HAWK.

1069
01:07:40,288 --> 01:07:43,392
DON'T YOU REALIZE
I HAVE TO ARREST YOU?

1070
01:07:43,425 --> 01:07:45,727
[ CLICKS TONGUE ]

1071
01:07:45,760 --> 01:07:48,397
HOW COULD YOU DO THIS?

1072
01:07:48,430 --> 01:07:49,665
I TRUSTED YOU.

1073
01:07:50,732 --> 01:07:54,169
LOOK, LIZZIE,
I'M REALLY SORRY.

1074
01:07:54,202 --> 01:07:55,471
OH, SHIT.

1075
01:07:55,504 --> 01:07:57,873
ALL RIGHT.
LET'S HAVE IT.

1076
01:07:57,906 --> 01:08:00,409
EVERYTHING.

1077
01:08:00,442 --> 01:08:03,245
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

1078
01:08:07,149 --> 01:08:09,384
MY BROTHER WAS SET UP
BY A MAN NAMED GARR.

1079
01:08:09,417 --> 01:08:11,286
GARR?

1080
01:08:09,417 --> 01:08:11,286
<i> YEAH.</i>

1081
01:08:11,319 --> 01:08:13,355
THE SKINHEADS
WERE JUST BAIT.

1082
01:08:13,388 --> 01:08:16,492
<i> APPARENTLY GARR'S BEHIND
 ALL THE DISAPPEARANCES
 OF THE BA WONG.</i>

1083
01:08:16,524 --> 01:08:18,192
<i> SOLDIER WAS ONTO THEM.</i>

1084
01:08:18,225 --> 01:08:19,795
CLAY AND HIS BOYS WOULD TAKE
THE BA WONG TO GARR,

1085
01:08:19,828 --> 01:08:21,497
AND THEY'D JUST DISAPPEAR
FOR GOOD.

1086
01:08:23,732 --> 01:08:25,367
NOT FOR GOOD.

1087
01:08:25,399 --> 01:08:28,536
ONE OF THEM WASHED ASHORE
THE OTHER DAY.

1088
01:08:28,569 --> 01:08:30,371
I KNOW ALL ABOUT GARR,
THOUGH.

1089
01:08:31,439 --> 01:08:33,442
YOU DO?

1090
01:08:33,475 --> 01:08:35,377
HE'S AN EX-MARINE.

1091
01:08:35,410 --> 01:08:37,846
HE'S WHAT?

1092
01:08:39,214 --> 01:08:40,381
DID A TOUR OF MANILA,

1093
01:08:40,415 --> 01:08:42,384
WHERE HE HONED
HIS MARTIAL-ARTS SKILLS.

1094
01:08:42,417 --> 01:08:44,753
HE STUDIED WITH THE BEST.

1095
01:08:44,786 --> 01:08:46,455
THEN, IN '91,

1096
01:08:46,488 --> 01:08:48,657
CHARGED WITH RUNNING
A BLACK-MARKET ARMS RING.

1097
01:08:48,689 --> 01:08:50,358
NOW, THE MARINES
COULDN'T PROVE IT.

1098
01:08:50,392 --> 01:08:52,827
BUT THEY REQUESTED HE RESIGN
HIS COMMISSION.

1099
01:08:52,861 --> 01:08:55,497
SO HE CAME BACK HERE,
ESTABLISHED HIMSELF
IN THE RACKETS,

1100
01:08:55,529 --> 01:08:57,800
AND TODAY HE'S ONE OF
THE LEADING CRIME BOSSES
IN THE AREA.

1101
01:08:59,234 --> 01:09:02,204
I THINK IT'S TIME I HAD
A LITTLE CHAT WITH OUR MR. GARR,

1102
01:09:02,237 --> 01:09:03,739
MARINE TO MARINE.

1103
01:09:03,772 --> 01:09:07,309
DAMN IT, HAWK.
YOU CAN'T KEEP DOING THIS TO ME.

1104
01:09:07,341 --> 01:09:09,844
YOU SIT ON YOUR GODDAMN HANDS,
TAKE A VALIUM,

1105
01:09:09,877 --> 01:09:11,613
AND LET THE POLICE
HANDLE THIS.

1106
01:09:13,348 --> 01:09:15,417
I WILL ARREST YOU.

1107
01:09:15,450 --> 01:09:20,421
IS THAT CLEAR...CAPTAIN?

1108
01:09:20,455 --> 01:09:22,424
LIZZIE, LISTEN TO ME.

1109
01:09:22,457 --> 01:09:23,959
LISTEN FOR JUST A MOMENT.

1110
01:09:23,992 --> 01:09:27,596
RIGHT NOW YOU'RE BOUND BY A CODE
OF CONDUCT, AND I'M NOT,

1111
01:09:27,629 --> 01:09:29,965
WHICH MEANS IN SOME WAYS
I CAN BE MORE EFFECTIVE.

1112
01:09:29,997 --> 01:09:32,733
<i> IF YOU WANT TO ARREST ME,
 THEN GO AHEAD.</i>

1113
01:09:32,767 --> 01:09:36,371
BUT WAIT TILL AFTER WE NAIL
THIS BASTARD.

1114
01:09:38,740 --> 01:09:40,776
I'M LATE FOR WORK.

1115
01:09:47,381 --> 01:09:49,350
[ SIREN WAILING ]

1116
01:09:53,755 --> 01:09:55,424
[ WAILING STOPS ]

1117
01:10:19,581 --> 01:10:21,450
UH, GOOD DAY, OFFICER.

1118
01:10:21,483 --> 01:10:23,352
UH, CAN I HELP YOU?
IS SOMETHING WRONG?

1119
01:10:23,385 --> 01:10:25,020
THAT'S JUST WHAT I WAS
ABOUT TO ASK YOU.

1120
01:10:25,053 --> 01:10:27,990
YOU WERE DOING 25
IN A 60-MILE-PER-HOUR ZONE.

1121
01:10:28,023 --> 01:10:28,991
<i> UH...</i>

1122
01:10:29,024 --> 01:10:31,526
UH, JUST BEING CAREFUL.

1123
01:10:31,559 --> 01:10:33,962
CAN I SEE YOUR LICENSE
AND REGISTRATION?

1124
01:10:33,995 --> 01:10:35,397
SURE.

1125
01:10:40,702 --> 01:10:43,338
SO, WHAT'S THAT?

1126
01:10:43,371 --> 01:10:44,840
OH, THE COOLER?

1127
01:10:44,873 --> 01:10:47,009
UH, UH, IT'S --
IT'S A COOLER.

1128
01:10:47,042 --> 01:10:48,410
WHAT DO YOU GOT IN THERE?

1129
01:10:48,443 --> 01:10:50,980
NOTHING. NOTHING.
NOTHING.

1130
01:10:52,747 --> 01:10:55,617
UH, WAIT. THERE --
THERE'S NOTHING IN THERE.

1131
01:10:55,650 --> 01:10:57,318
REALLY?

1132
01:10:57,352 --> 01:10:59,488
TAKE A LOOK-SEE.

1133
01:11:09,364 --> 01:11:10,632
STEP OUT OF THE CAR.

1134
01:11:09,364 --> 01:11:10,632
RIGHT.

1135
01:11:10,665 --> 01:11:12,801
STEP OUT OF THE CAR SLOWLY.

1136
01:11:10,665 --> 01:11:12,801
YEAH. DON'T SHOOT.

1137
01:11:12,834 --> 01:11:15,404
STEP OUT OF THE CAR.

1138
01:11:12,834 --> 01:11:15,404
I'M...

1139
01:11:15,437 --> 01:11:16,472
STEP OUT.

1140
01:11:15,437 --> 01:11:16,472
YEAH.

1141
01:11:16,505 --> 01:11:18,640
JUST DON'T -- DON'T SHOOT.

1142
01:11:16,505 --> 01:11:18,640
TURN AROUND RIGHT HERE.

1143
01:11:18,673 --> 01:11:21,009
UP AGAINST THE CAR.
UP AGAINST THE CAR.

1144
01:11:21,042 --> 01:11:22,511
TURN AROUND.

1145
01:11:22,544 --> 01:11:24,446
OKAY, REMEMBER,
WHEN YOU USE YOUR FLASH-BANG,

1146
01:11:24,479 --> 01:11:26,915
CLOSE YOUR EYES, OR YOU'LL BE
JUST AS BAD OFF AS YOUR ENEMIES.

1147
01:11:26,948 --> 01:11:28,784
DON'T KILL ANYBODY.
YOU READ ME?

1148
01:11:34,789 --> 01:11:36,391
NOW, WHAT'S THE PLAN?

1149
01:11:36,424 --> 01:11:37,826
QUICK AND CLEAN,
IN AND OUT.

1150
01:11:37,859 --> 01:11:40,362
IF MY BOYS ARE INSIDE,
SPLIT UP, CALL THE COPS.

1151
01:11:40,395 --> 01:11:43,098
IF NOT,
TOSS A COUPLE FLASH-BANGS,

1152
01:11:43,131 --> 01:11:45,367
GRAB A HOSTAGE,
TRY TO GET HIM TO BLAB.

1153
01:11:45,400 --> 01:11:46,634
HEY, PRETTY GOOD.

1154
01:11:46,668 --> 01:11:48,637
DID YOU EVER THINK OF JOINING
YOUR MARINES?

1155
01:11:48,670 --> 01:11:50,472
FUCK, NO, SIR.

1156
01:11:50,505 --> 01:11:52,007
SMART MAN.

1157
01:11:53,441 --> 01:11:55,477
LET'S JAM.

1158
01:12:08,990 --> 01:12:10,959
[ GRUNTS ]

1159
01:12:08,990 --> 01:12:10,959
[ CASING CLINKS ]

1160
01:12:10,992 --> 01:12:12,428
[ GUNSHOT ]

1161
01:12:37,752 --> 01:12:39,455
[ GROANING ]

1162
01:12:49,831 --> 01:12:51,834
[ GRUNTS ]

1163
01:12:57,872 --> 01:12:59,408
AAH!

1164
01:13:20,995 --> 01:13:24,499
HELLO.
I'M DR. PALMER.

1165
01:13:24,532 --> 01:13:26,201
I'M GOING TO HAVE TO
TISSUE-TYPE YOU BOTH.

1166
01:13:26,234 --> 01:13:28,570
DON'T WORRY.
IT WON'T HURT.

1167
01:13:28,603 --> 01:13:32,441
<i> HEY, DOC...
 MAKE IT HURT.</i>

1168
01:13:36,478 --> 01:13:40,149
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS,
TELEPHONES RINGING ]

1169
01:13:43,551 --> 01:13:45,554
DID YOU HEAR?

1170
01:13:45,587 --> 01:13:46,221
HEAR WHAT?

1171
01:13:46,254 --> 01:13:48,490
ABOUT THE HEART.

1172
01:13:56,564 --> 01:13:58,700
[ BEEPING ]

1173
01:14:00,502 --> 01:14:01,736
HE'S PERFECT.

1174
01:14:01,769 --> 01:14:04,506
WE COULDN'T ASK
FOR A BETTER DONOR.

1175
01:14:04,539 --> 01:14:07,209
[ LAUGHS ]

1176
01:14:04,539 --> 01:14:07,209
THIS IS JOY.

1177
01:14:07,242 --> 01:14:09,711
A MILLION DOLLARS.

1178
01:14:09,744 --> 01:14:11,713
MMM.
[ LAUGHS ]

1179
01:14:15,283 --> 01:14:17,486
PREP HIM FOR SURGERY.

1180
01:14:17,519 --> 01:14:19,020
I'M GONNA GET SIEGEL.

1181
01:14:19,053 --> 01:14:21,590
HE WANTS TO PICK IT UP
HIMSELF.

1182
01:14:25,226 --> 01:14:26,193
[ GRUNTS ]

1183
01:14:26,227 --> 01:14:27,229
EASY DOES IT, MAN.

1184
01:14:27,262 --> 01:14:29,097
THAT'S OKAY.
I'M FINE.

1185
01:14:29,130 --> 01:14:32,668
[ GRUNTS, SIGHS ]

1186
01:14:34,235 --> 01:14:36,772
OKAY,
I'LL REST A MINUTE.

1187
01:14:38,840 --> 01:14:40,275
ONE OF YOU GUYS LIPING?

1188
01:14:40,308 --> 01:14:43,011
YO, WHO THE HELL
ARE YOU?

1189
01:14:43,044 --> 01:14:44,646
I'M HAWK.

1190
01:14:44,679 --> 01:14:45,947
WHERE'S LIPO?

1191
01:14:45,980 --> 01:14:47,115
<i> LIPO?</i>

1192
01:14:47,148 --> 01:14:48,216
HERE?

1193
01:14:47,148 --> 01:14:48,216
<i> YEAH.</i>

1194
01:14:48,249 --> 01:14:49,951
WE CAME IN TOGETHER.

1195
01:14:49,984 --> 01:14:50,952
SHIT!

1196
01:14:50,985 --> 01:14:52,187
WE HAVEN'T SEEN HIM, MAN.

1197
01:14:52,220 --> 01:14:54,189
THEY THREW YOU IN HERE
A WHILE AGO.

1198
01:14:56,190 --> 01:14:57,659
<i> THEY, UH...</i>

1199
01:14:57,692 --> 01:15:00,195
THEY DID THAT TO ALL OF US.

1200
01:15:00,228 --> 01:15:02,531
NICE LITTLE CHUNKS MISSING.

1201
01:15:10,705 --> 01:15:12,674
YOU CAN FORGET IT, MAN.

1202
01:15:12,707 --> 01:15:15,243
WE'VE BEEN OVER THIS PLACE
A THOUSAND TIMES.

1203
01:15:15,276 --> 01:15:17,077
AIN'T NO WAY OUT OF HERE.

1204
01:15:17,111 --> 01:15:19,281
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]
INDULGE ME.

1205
01:15:23,952 --> 01:15:24,820
ALL RIGHT.

1206
01:15:24,853 --> 01:15:27,255
YOU GUYS FINALLY DECIDED
TO LET ME GO.

1207
01:15:27,288 --> 01:15:29,223
REALLY APPRECIATE IT.

1208
01:15:31,759 --> 01:15:34,195
SIR? HELLO?

1209
01:15:34,228 --> 01:15:35,230
HELLO?

1210
01:15:37,765 --> 01:15:40,068
DOES ANYBODY HAVE A LIGHTER?

1211
01:15:40,101 --> 01:15:41,803
THEY TOOK EVERYTHING, MAN.

1212
01:15:41,836 --> 01:15:45,273
I, UH, GOT THESE MATCHES.

1213
01:15:45,306 --> 01:15:47,241
GREAT.

1214
01:15:47,275 --> 01:15:50,045
UH, HANG ON TO THOSE
FOR A BIT.

1215
01:15:50,078 --> 01:15:52,214
LIPING, HOLD THESE.

1216
01:16:05,360 --> 01:16:07,228
SOMEBODY GRAB THAT BULB.

1217
01:16:11,366 --> 01:16:14,703
YO, MAN,
WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU DOING?

1218
01:16:18,039 --> 01:16:19,374
IS THAT REAL GOLD?

1219
01:16:19,407 --> 01:16:22,611
DAMN RIGHT, IT'S REAL.
18 KARAT.

1220
01:16:22,644 --> 01:16:25,247
OH, NO. NOT MY CHAIN.
NO WAY.

1221
01:16:42,397 --> 01:16:45,300
WHAT THE HELL YOU DOING
UP AND AROUND?

1222
01:16:47,268 --> 01:16:50,172
DON'T YOU EVEN
FUCKING TALK TO ME.

1223
01:16:55,176 --> 01:16:57,345
OH, JEEZ.

1224
01:16:57,378 --> 01:17:00,014
[ GRUNTS ]

1225
01:17:00,048 --> 01:17:02,183
[ ZIPPER OPENS ]

1226
01:17:02,216 --> 01:17:04,686
[ DUQUESNE FARTING, DEFECATING ]

1227
01:17:04,719 --> 01:17:06,788
<i> OH, MAN.</i>

1228
01:17:06,821 --> 01:17:08,624
MAN.

1229
01:17:06,821 --> 01:17:08,624
<i> [ GRUNTS ]</i>

1230
01:17:53,935 --> 01:17:55,136
IS THIS GOOD?

1231
01:17:55,169 --> 01:17:57,272
NO, LIPING.
IT'S GOT TO BE FINER.

1232
01:17:57,305 --> 01:17:59,307
MAKE IT AS FINE
AS YOU CAN GET IT, OKAY?

1233
01:18:00,842 --> 01:18:03,777
AND THEN WE NEED SHRAPNEL --
ANYTHING SMALL, SHARP.

1234
01:18:03,811 --> 01:18:05,246
ANYTHING YOU CAN FIND.

1235
01:18:05,279 --> 01:18:06,748
OKAY, LOOK AROUND.

1236
01:18:59,100 --> 01:19:01,035
<i> Liping:
 IS THIS GONNA WOR?</i>

1237
01:19:01,068 --> 01:19:04,205
I'LL BE DAMNED IF I KNOW.

1238
01:19:04,238 --> 01:19:06,341
YOU GUYS READY?

1239
01:19:06,374 --> 01:19:08,242
OKAY, GO.

1240
01:19:12,146 --> 01:19:13,348
HEY! OPEN UP!

1241
01:19:13,381 --> 01:19:15,784
THIS GUY JUST DIED!

1242
01:19:15,817 --> 01:19:18,320
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

1243
01:19:22,890 --> 01:19:24,526
[ LATCH CLICKS ]

1244
01:19:26,460 --> 01:19:28,263
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLES ]

1245
01:19:29,897 --> 01:19:32,167
[ MAN GROANING ]

1246
01:19:35,269 --> 01:19:37,205
COME ON.
LET'S GO.

1247
01:19:37,238 --> 01:19:39,975
[ GROANING ]

1248
01:19:56,557 --> 01:19:58,559
ONE PEEP,
AND YOU'RE SWISS CHEESE.

1249
01:19:59,460 --> 01:20:00,328
HELP!

1250
01:20:00,361 --> 01:20:01,363
[ GRUNTS ]

1251
01:20:05,333 --> 01:20:06,433
<i> [ GRUNTS ]</i>

1252
01:20:08,569 --> 01:20:10,038
ALL RIGHT, HAWK!

1253
01:20:10,071 --> 01:20:11,573
THAT'S MY PAL HAWK!

1254
01:20:11,606 --> 01:20:13,842
HEAR THAT?
YOU'RE ALL GOING DOWN.

1255
01:20:13,875 --> 01:20:16,444
IF I WERE Y'ALL, I'D BEAT FEET
OUT OF HERE BEFORE IT'S...

1256
01:20:16,477 --> 01:20:17,579
[ GAS HISSING ]

1257
01:20:17,612 --> 01:20:19,347
WHAT THE HELL WAS THAT?

1258
01:20:19,380 --> 01:20:23,151
I DON'T KNOW, BUT I SURE HOPE
THEY'RE ON OUR SIDE.

1259
01:20:39,467 --> 01:20:41,335
GOT TO LEAVE HIM, LIPING.

1260
01:20:43,337 --> 01:20:46,107
COME ON.
LET'S GO.

1261
01:21:07,461 --> 01:21:08,563
COME ON, MAN!

1262
01:21:08,596 --> 01:21:09,464
THE PLACE IS BEING SHOT UP,

1263
01:21:09,497 --> 01:21:11,432
AND YOU'RE FUCKING SITTING
ON THE BOWL!

1264
01:21:11,465 --> 01:21:12,400
<i> [ DEFECATING ]</i>

1265
01:21:12,433 --> 01:21:14,102
<i> CAN'T HELP IT, MAN.</i>

1266
01:21:14,135 --> 01:21:16,404
<i> THESE PILLS GIVE ME
 THE RUNS.</i>

1267
01:21:16,437 --> 01:21:17,906
<i> YOU GO AHEAD.</i>

1268
01:21:17,939 --> 01:21:20,275
COME ON, MAN,
I'M NOT GOING OUT THERE ALONE.

1269
01:21:20,308 --> 01:21:21,409
<i> ALL RIGHT.</i>

1270
01:21:21,442 --> 01:21:24,613
[ DOOR RATTLING ]

1271
01:21:47,401 --> 01:21:49,037
I ALMOST KILLED YOU.

1272
01:21:49,070 --> 01:21:50,571
<i> YEAH, WELL,
 I'M GLAD TO SEE YOU.</i>

1273
01:21:50,604 --> 01:21:52,607
WAS THAT YOU MAKING
ALL THAT RACKET DOWN THERE?

1274
01:21:52,640 --> 01:21:55,109
YEAH, BUT I DON'T KNOW
HOW MANY OF THEM ARE LEFT.

1275
01:21:55,142 --> 01:21:56,477
WELL, I'M SURE
WE'RE GONNA FIND OUT.

1276
01:21:56,510 --> 01:21:58,580
COME ON.
LET'S GO.

1277
01:21:59,714 --> 01:22:02,417
[ MACHINERY BEEPING ]

1278
01:22:06,187 --> 01:22:07,322
POLICE OFFICER!
FREEZE!

1279
01:22:07,355 --> 01:22:08,356
LIPO!

1280
01:22:08,390 --> 01:22:10,959
GET THE HELL AWAY
FROM MY BROTHER, YOU BITCH!

1281
01:22:10,992 --> 01:22:11,960
[ GASPING ]

1282
01:22:11,993 --> 01:22:13,494
I'M GONNA KILL YOU!

1283
01:22:13,527 --> 01:22:15,330
OH!

1284
01:22:19,433 --> 01:22:21,036
[ GRUNTS ]

1285
01:22:22,336 --> 01:22:24,239
[ GUN CLICKS ]

1286
01:22:25,373 --> 01:22:28,409
DON'T MOVE!

1287
01:22:28,442 --> 01:22:29,477
KEEP 'EM UP.

1288
01:22:36,751 --> 01:22:38,386
[ GRUNTS ]

1289
01:23:14,221 --> 01:23:15,991
[ GLASS BREAKING ]

1290
01:23:29,336 --> 01:23:30,638
[ GRUNTS ]

1291
01:24:10,511 --> 01:24:11,813
BITCH.

1292
01:24:13,781 --> 01:24:15,450
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLING ]

1293
01:24:15,483 --> 01:24:18,186
[ SCREAMING ]

1294
01:24:18,219 --> 01:24:20,722
[ GLASS BREAKING,
METAL RATTLING ]

1295
01:24:33,501 --> 01:24:36,471
[ GROWLING ]

1296
01:24:36,504 --> 01:24:38,139
[ SAW BUZZING ]

1297
01:24:46,447 --> 01:24:49,517
[ GASPS, SCREAMS ]

1298
01:24:52,386 --> 01:24:54,389
<i> COME ON!</i>

1299
01:25:01,362 --> 01:25:02,463
COME ON.

1300
01:25:02,496 --> 01:25:04,332
[ GRUNTS ]
I'M OKAY. I CAN WALK.

1301
01:25:04,365 --> 01:25:05,733
GET YOUR GUN.

1302
01:25:04,365 --> 01:25:05,733
OKAY.

1303
01:25:09,336 --> 01:25:10,638
OKAY, LET'S GO.

1304
01:25:10,671 --> 01:25:12,540
COME ON.
LET'S GO.

1305
01:25:15,576 --> 01:25:17,712
COME ON, LADS.
NO TIME FOR A REUNION.

1306
01:25:17,745 --> 01:25:20,548
LET'S GO.
THERE'S THE FRONT DOOR.

1307
01:25:22,316 --> 01:25:24,519
THE ROOF.
IT'S QUICKER.

1308
01:25:33,494 --> 01:25:35,330
COME ON!

1309
01:25:40,568 --> 01:25:42,503
SO WHAT IS IT NOW?

1310
01:25:42,536 --> 01:25:43,738
JUST HAND IT OVER.

1311
01:25:43,771 --> 01:25:44,739
WHAT?

1312
01:25:44,772 --> 01:25:46,374
YOU KNOW WHAT.

1313
01:25:46,407 --> 01:25:47,441
THIS?

1314
01:25:47,474 --> 01:25:49,310
YEAH.
GIVE IT OVER.

1315
01:25:49,343 --> 01:25:50,778
IT WAS A FUCKING ACCIDENT,
MAN.

1316
01:25:50,811 --> 01:25:53,447
WELL, YOU'RE A MENACE
WITH IT.

1317
01:25:53,480 --> 01:25:55,215
USE YOUR PIECE.

1318
01:26:11,365 --> 01:26:12,833
<i> GOTCHA!</i>

1319
01:26:12,866 --> 01:26:15,670
[ GRUNTS ]

1320
01:26:17,605 --> 01:26:18,572
[ Weakly ]
FUCKER.

1321
01:26:18,606 --> 01:26:21,608
OW! AAH!

1322
01:26:29,316 --> 01:26:31,619
[ BONES CRACK, BLADE GRUNTS ]

1323
01:26:34,588 --> 01:26:37,759
[ BREATHING RAGGEDLY ]

1324
01:26:48,402 --> 01:26:50,404
<i> COSTA RICA, HUH?</i>

1325
01:26:50,437 --> 01:26:52,506
MY STEPBROTHER JACK AND I
VACATIONED THERE

1326
01:26:52,539 --> 01:26:54,675
ON OUR LAST LEAVE.

1327
01:26:54,708 --> 01:26:56,911
BAHíA DE CORONADO.

1328
01:26:56,944 --> 01:26:59,480
<i> GORGEOUS PLACE.</i>

1329
01:26:59,513 --> 01:27:02,750
IN FACT, I'M THINKING OF
GOING THERE ON MY NEXT VACATION.

1330
01:27:02,783 --> 01:27:04,819
[ EXHALES SLOWLY ]

1331
01:27:11,759 --> 01:27:14,229
COME ON.
LET'S GO.

1332
01:27:38,919 --> 01:27:40,388
ELIAS GARR?

1333
01:27:40,421 --> 01:27:42,490
IN THE FLESH.

1334
01:27:42,523 --> 01:27:45,493
YOU'RE COMING WITH ME.

1335
01:27:45,526 --> 01:27:47,795
OF COURSE,
YOU'LL HAVE TO KILL ME FIRST.

1336
01:28:01,342 --> 01:28:03,478
IT'S TIME.

1337
01:28:13,520 --> 01:28:15,523
BRING IT AROUND!
BRING IT AROUND!

1338
01:28:49,390 --> 01:28:51,759
[ GRUNTS ]

1339
01:29:02,703 --> 01:29:04,372
AAH!

1340
01:29:08,942 --> 01:29:10,611
OH!

1341
01:29:42,509 --> 01:29:44,612
AAH!

1342
01:29:52,686 --> 01:29:53,688
AAH!

1343
01:30:18,846 --> 01:30:20,181
AAH!

1344
01:30:30,090 --> 01:30:32,493
DON'T OVEREXTEND YOURSELF,
MARINE.

1345
01:30:32,526 --> 01:30:33,827
[ LAUGHS ]

1346
01:30:38,532 --> 01:30:39,200
AAH!

1347
01:31:15,002 --> 01:31:15,503
AAH!

1348
01:31:15,536 --> 01:31:18,539
[ BLADES SQUEAKING ]

1349
01:31:41,094 --> 01:31:43,164
[ SIRENS WAILING ]

1350
01:31:51,338 --> 01:31:54,008
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

1351
01:31:58,211 --> 01:32:02,116
MAN...I DON'T KNOW
HOW TO THANK YOU.

1352
01:32:02,149 --> 01:32:03,751
ME NEITHER, MAN.

1353
01:32:03,784 --> 01:32:06,853
YOU NOT ONLY SAVED MY LIFE,
YOU KICKED MAJOR ASS.

1354
01:32:06,887 --> 01:32:08,188
[ CHUCKLES ]

1355
01:32:08,221 --> 01:32:10,558
WELL, KICKING ASS IS
WHAT IT'S ALL ABOUT, RIGHT?

1356
01:32:13,160 --> 01:32:16,330
OKAY, YOU GUYS.
LET'S GO.

1357
01:32:16,363 --> 01:32:18,299
WE GOT SOME QUESTIONS ABOUT
WHAT HAPPENED BACK THERE.

1358
01:32:16,363 --> 01:32:18,299
SO...

1359
01:32:18,332 --> 01:32:19,967
WHAT NOW?

1360
01:32:20,000 --> 01:32:21,035
YOU HAVE ANY PLANS?

1361
01:32:21,068 --> 01:32:24,105
SEEMS TO ME THIS TOWN'S GOT
A LOT OF POSSIBILITIES.

1362
01:32:26,340 --> 01:32:28,576
<i> Lt. Durkee:
 DETECTIVE HAMPTON?</i>

1363
01:32:36,016 --> 01:32:38,052
FINE WORK ON THIS.

1364
01:32:38,085 --> 01:32:40,021
<i> I'M PUTTING YOU UP
 FOR A COMMENDATION.</i>

1365
01:32:41,855 --> 01:32:44,224
THANKS, LIEU --
MEANS A LOT.

1366
01:32:44,858 --> 01:32:46,260
AND THANKS TO YOU, KELLY.

1367
01:32:46,293 --> 01:32:48,829
<i> YOU HAVE A GOOD TRIP
 BACK TO ENGLAND.</i>

1368
01:32:48,862 --> 01:32:50,097
<i> AND IF EVER YOU'RE BACK
 IN TOWN, YOU MAKE SURE --</i>

1369
01:32:50,130 --> 01:32:52,199
LIEU, UH,
HAWK WAS JUST SAYING

1370
01:32:52,232 --> 01:32:55,269
HE WAS THINKING ABOUT
STICKING AROUND.

1371
01:32:55,302 --> 01:32:56,637
WHAT?

1372
01:32:56,670 --> 01:32:58,205
YEAH,
THIS TOWN NEEDS A MARINE.

1373
01:32:58,238 --> 01:33:00,274
IN FACT, I'M THINKING
OF JOINING THE FORCE.

1374
01:33:00,307 --> 01:33:01,842
<i> I'VE GOT DUAL CITIZENSHIP,
 YOU KNOW.</i>

1375
01:33:01,875 --> 01:33:03,911
[ Chuckling ] NOW, YOU JUST --
YOU JUST WAIT A MINUTE.

1376
01:33:03,944 --> 01:33:06,080
CAN I REQUEST ASSIGNMENT
TO THE 44th?

1377
01:33:06,113 --> 01:33:08,616
I DON'T SEE WHY NOT.
LIEU?

1378
01:33:12,085 --> 01:33:14,822
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

1379
01:33:21,328 --> 01:33:23,331
CATCH YOU LATER.

1380
01:33:26,366 --> 01:33:29,704
[ MID-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS ]

